{"type":"message","id":"08ce10de","parentId":"1f542064","timestamp":"2026-03-09T21:02:20.956Z","message":{"role":"user","content":[{"type":"text","text":"[Mon 2026-03-09 16:02 CDT] [Subagent Context] You are running as a subagent (depth 1/1). Results auto-announce to your requester; do not busy-poll for status.\n\n[Subagent Task]: Message for Jared: Tony says he loves the team. Start now on RevOps pipeline: propose 5 pipeline actions for lead handling and follow-up discipline."}],"timestamp":1773090140953}}
{"type":"message","id":"8f4db98a","parentId":"08ce10de","timestamp":"2026-03-09T21:02:24.807Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"text","text":"Message for Jared:\nTony says he loves the team.\n\nHere are 5 proposed pipeline actions for lead handling and follow-up discipline in RevOps:\n\n1. Lead Qualification: Implement a standardized lead scoring system to prioritize leads based on engagement, fit, and buying intent. This helps sales focus on high-potential leads first.\n\n2. Automated Lead Assignment: Use rules to assign leads automatically to appropriate sales reps or teams based on criteria like territory, product interest, or lead source to ensure timely follow-up.\n\n3. Multi-Touch Follow-Up Sequence: Develop a timed sequence of outreach actions (calls, emails, LinkedIn touches) after lead capture, ensuring consistent and persistent engagement over a set period.\n\n4. Lead Status Updates: Enforce regular updates on lead status in the CRM, with alerts for leads stuck in stages too long, enabling pipeline hygiene and removal of stale leads.\n\n5. Post-Meeting Follow-Up: Standardize a follow-up process immediately after sales meetings or demos, including customized messages and next-step scheduling to maintain momentum.\n\nLet me know if you want these refined or expanded.","textSignature":"{\"v\":1,\"id\":\"msg_028cac9ce1904fc70069af355db2b0819486250549881534c0\"}"}],"api":"openai-responses","provider":"openai","model":"gpt-4.1-mini","usage":{"input":8500,"output":220,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":8720,"cost":{"input":0.0034000000000000002,"output":0.00035200000000000005,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0.003752}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1773090140955}}
